&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: none 0s ease 0s; display: block;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          INTRODUCTION
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
      
                      
           Don’t you often feel lost when people start using acronyms and terms that you do not have a clue what it means?
          
                    &#xD;
    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
      &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
      
                      
           Some of us just either try to change the topic or even slowly back down and find another conversation we can make sense what people are talking about. &amp;#55357;&amp;#56842;
          
                    &#xD;
    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          If you are like me, you would just want to know what it means and ask the question that nobody wants, even if the rest is staring at you as if you need to know everything…
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Please tell me I am not alone…
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
                      
           WHAT IS LEAD GENERATION
          
                    &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          The term “LEAD GENERATION” was one of those for me back in the day… This term was born recently (I would want to comfort myself it was recently &amp;#55357;&amp;#56842;), especially on Digital platforms…Everything these days wherever you go is just Digital…
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          The problem is, if you are not either within the industry or making use of the industry on a personal basis or within your own business, whether you have a small one-man-band or a large corporate, you are losing ground against everyone around you…and that just simply means you are making less and less profit…yip that means a declining business.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Everyone knows where that is headed…we see so many of these around us closing their doors.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Who would not want more clients? We have a unique LEAD GENERATION STRATEGY where we use all avenues of social media to generate high-quality leads at exceptional high conversions rates…LET us show you how…
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div style="transition: opacity 1s ease-in-out 0s;" data-rss-type="text"&gt;&#xD;
  
                  
         Allow me to explain a bit further….
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Interesting stats from Google is that they are predicting that if a business does not generate at least 25% of their Turnover through an Online channel within the next 5 years, the chances of surviving in the upcoming 10 years are almost not possible.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          makes this new era in business unobtainable to explore for most SME’s are the fact that the services of Digital agencies are just simply unaffordable, to put it mildly, which leaves the owners/management of the SME’s to explore these digital opportunities themselves.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Often, they chose not to explore due to the fear of failure or if they explore, 97% of the time they fail because of the lack of skills or even resources.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          You see, times are changing and it’s changing fast, which means all of us to need to decide sooner rather than later.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          You might be thinking, I am doing well in Digital through Facebook posts or the ad-hoc comments on their Facebook pages.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          If you were like me, where I thought the Digital Lead Generation is where you:
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Get likes on your Facebook page
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Engage with your audience on your page through doing at least 2 posts per day (as certain experts still proclaim)
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          I Can assure you, we were in “Pre-School” when it comes to Digital Media advertising, not to mention lead generation. 
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          So many of us have had the experience where we have the social media interactions (likes, clicks, comments and even shares), but we do not see any increase in our Turnover or we cannot measure any Return on Investment and we are stuck with the same customer scenario where 20% of our customer generate 80% of our turnover…this obviously is a problem.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Unless you're in a fortunate position of not wanting or needing more of the 20% customers above, you'll find that nearly every business has one question in mind: How do you get more customers?
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          And more importantly, how do you acquire them cost-effectively?
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          The answer is a customised lead generation plan for your business.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
                      
           WHAT IS A LEAD? 
          
                    &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          A lead is a qualified customer enquiry - someone reaching out to you saying 'Yes, I'm interested in your business! Please contact me'. – YES, They beg you to offer your product/service to them!!
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;b&gt;&#xD;
      
                      
           WHAT IS LEAD GENERATION? 
          
                    &#xD;
    &lt;/b&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Lead generation is the process we follow to: 
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Find the people who are interested in your services
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          inform them about your business
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          get them to fill out a contact form online, or pop into your shop and buy your products.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          You see we have a PROVEN strategy with limited risk which all the large digital Marketing Agencies are charging an arm and a leg, which makes it unaffordable to the smaller companies. 
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          We often have Clients that are sceptical in the beginning and within a matter of weeks, they cannot stop singing our praises….and Yes, we are able to generate leads B2B as well as B2C (Sorry there I do the acronym thing...B2B = Business to Business and B2C = Business to Customer)
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          If you are interested in getting on a short Strategy call, Click below and we will make time to explain all your questions in detail and also discuss the details.
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          I have to go and get to understand why the campaign we are running currently are generating 36 leads a day at a cost of R4.71 a lead. The clients are over the moon and so are we...if only people knew more how to do this...lucky us...we have the formula just right
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Until we meet again my fellow lead-genners...
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    
                    
          Will
         
                  &#xD;
  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;
  &lt;div&gt;&#xD;
    &lt;br/&gt;&#xD;
